features: 🛬[Based On The Real Plane] Crelloci airplane imitates the genuine Airbus A380 model plane. With a realistic tail, wings, and engines. The top of the aircraft can be opened to view the body inside. Realistic simulation of the scene in the cabin, your kids will think they’re flying like real pilots!

💨[Pull Back & Release] This toy airplane has a pulled-back and release function. No batteries are needed to fuel the fun. Just pull back an airplane toy and watch it race across the floor. Kids would be thrilled with the bump-and-go aspect.

✅[Premium Quality Airplane] Made from premium quality durable alloy and plastic. The child-friendly design means the 3-year-old's toy is safe to use for all the passionate play indoors and out. Toy Airplane Size: Length 8.66*7.48*2.76 Inches.

🌟[Lights Up & Sounds Effect] Gently press the head of the airplane toy, and the lights would flash along with the sound effect of the airliner taking off. Kids would be delighted by the additional highlights.

🎉[Great Gift for Kids] Airplane toys are a great opportunity to spend quality time with little ones. They also foster independence during solo play and social skills during group play. This pull-back airplane toy would make a wonderful present to the children for all festive occasions such as Birthdays, Christmas, Halloween, Thanksgiving, New Year, and more!
